BT /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 595.0 Tm (The application is split into a React frontend and a PHP backend API with a MySQL) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 581.5 Tm (database. The frontend talks to the backend through the /api path.) Tj ET
